{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_11","type":"agent_message","text":"The local pattern files did not show an applicable DOSDP pattern for these squamous epithelium definitions. I found three named squamous epithelium classes using `has_part CL:0000076`; changing only the parent would likely stop simple/stratified squamous epithelium from classifying under it, so I’m checking those stanzas as alignment candidates."}}
